.za/Soccer/PSL/antipas-chiefs-katsvairo-must-step-up-his-game-20170116-2|title=Antipas: Chief's Katsvairo must step up his game|website=sport24.co.za}}</ref>\n\n==Club career==\nBack in [[Chicken Inn F.C.|Chicken Inn FC]], he managed a total of 14 goals in [[2015-16 Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League|2015-16]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newzimbabwe.com/sports-33206-SA+Katsvairo+expects+the+goals+to+come/sports.aspx|title=Katsvairo expects the goals to come|website=newzimbabwe.com}}</ref>\nJoining from [[Chicken Inn F.C.]] in the summer, Katsvairo enhanced [[Kaizer Chiefs FC]]'s striking options.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iol.co.za/sport/soccer/psl/komphela-banking-on-katsvairo-2071895|title=Komphela banking on Katsvairo|website=iol.co.za}}</ref> He made his league debut for the club on 14 September 2016 in a 1-1 home draw with [[Platinum Stars F.C.]]. He was subbed on for [[Lucky Baloyi]] in the 67th minute.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/09/14/south-africa/psl/kaizer-chiefs/platinum-stars/2325260/|title=Kaizer Chiefs vs. Platinum Stars \u2013 14 September 2016 \u2013 Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref> He scored his first goal against [[Free State Stars]] to secure a 2-0 win. His goal came in the 63rd minute.<ref>http://www.supersport.com/football/article.aspx?Id=3722384</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/09/28/south-africa/psl/free-state-stars/kaizer-chiefs/2325287/|title=Free State Stars vs. Kaizer Chiefs \u2013 28 September 2016 \u2013 Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.flashscores.co.uk/player/katsvairo-michelle/IexqdsMC/ Michelle Katsvairo] at Flashscore\n*[https://www.whoscored.com/Players/323300/Show/Michelle-Katsvairo Michelle Katsvairo] at Who Scored\n*{{Soccerway|mitchell-katsvairo/235371}}\n*[https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/286938-michelle-katsvairo Michelle Katsvairo] at Footballdatabase\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Katsvairo, Michelle}}\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Black Mambas F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Gunners F.C. players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Platinum players]]\n[[Category:Chicken Inn F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Kaizer Chiefs F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Singida United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:CAPS United players]]\n[[Category:Free State Stars F.C. players]]\n[[Category:South African Premier Division players]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in Tanzania]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in South Africa]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Tanzania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in South Africa]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n\n|name         = Michelle Katsvairo\n|birth_date   = {{Birth date and age|1990|5|5}}\n|birth_place  = [[Mutoko]], Zimbabwe\n|height       = 1.73m\n|position     = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub  = [[Ngezi Platinum F.C.|Ngezi Platinum]]\n|clubnumber   = \n|years1       = 2009\u20132010\n|clubs1       = [[Black Mambas F.C.|Black Mambas]]\n|caps1        =\n|goals1       =\n|years2       = 2011\n|clubs2       = [[Gunners F.C.|Gunners]]\n|caps2        =\n|goals2       =\n|years3       = 2012\u20132014\n|clubs3       = [[Platinum FC|Platinum]]\n|caps3        =\n|goals3       =\n|years4       = 2015\u20132016\n|clubs4       = [[Chicken Inn F.C.|Chicken Inn]]\n|caps4        =\n|goals4       =\n|years5       = 2016\u20132018\n|clubs5       = [[Kaizer Chiefs F.C.|Kaizer Chiefs]]\n|caps5        = 12\n|goals5       = 1\n|years6       = 2017\u20132018\n|clubs6       = \u2192 [[Singida United F.C.|Singida United]] (loan)\n|caps6        = \n|goals6       = \n|years7       = 2018\n|clubs7       = [[CAPS United F.C.|CAPS United]]\n|caps7        = 1\n|goal